wide%20range%20of%20outcomes%2C%20it's%20a%20highly%20speculative%20exercise.%20But%20on%20a%20directional%20basis%2C%20it's%20an%20important%20guidepost%20for%20investors.%20The%20ones%20that%20do%20their%20homework%20can%20compare%20the%20various%20theses%20and%20see%20who%20they%20align%20most%20closely%20with%2C%20then%20follow%20that%20strategist's%20calls%20all%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt's%20like%20college%20football's%20preseason%20rankings.%20A%20helpful%20guide%2C%20but%20not%20set%20in%20stone.%20(Look%20at%20Penn%20State%2C%20which%20started%20the%20season%20ranked%20%232%20in%20the%20country%20and%20finished%206-6.%20Yikes!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20it's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20analysts%20underestimated%20the%20S%26amp%3BP's%20performance%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20which%20is%20perhaps%20why%20they've%20gotten%20so%20aggressive%20for%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJoe%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%2C%20it's%20very%20possible%20that%20they're%20overcorrecting%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2026-stock-market-outlook-forecase-jpmorgan-morgan-stanley-spx-targets-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eundershooting%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20the%20last%20two%20years%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Wall%20Street%20was%20collectively%2018%25%20off%20the%20mark%20in%202024%2C%20and%20while%20they've%20been%20better%20this%20year%2C%20they're%20still%20lagging%20by%204%25.%20But%20they%20have%20been%20directionally%20correct.%20Ultimately%2C%20it's%20a%20better%20move%20to%20pick%20a%20strategist%20or%20two%20to%20follow%2C%20rather%20than%20try%20to%20obey%20the%20entire%20hive%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrategist%20forecasts%20have%20been%20like%20Indiana%20football.%20Picked%20to%20finish%2020th%20in%20the%20nation%2C%20they're%20now%20the%20top-ranked%20team%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20other%20interesting%20wrinkle%20is%20the%20Fed.%20We're%20getting%20a%20new%20chair%20%E2%80%94%20Thanks%20for%20the%20memories%2C%20Jerome!%20%E2%80%94%20and%20all%20the%20potential%20complications%20that%20come%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJoe%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat's%20absolutely%20a%20key%20factor%2C%20and%20the%20top%20wild%20card%20of%202026.%20There's%20a%20growing%20view%20that%20the%20new%20Fed%20chair%20will%20do%20Trump%20a%20solid%20and%20cut%20rates%20at%20will.%20That%20economic%20stimulus%20actually%20underpins%20the%20lofty%20earnings-growth%20forecasts%20most%20major%20firms%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-outlook-2026-inflation-debt-ai-bubble-bursts-tech-stocks-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EApollo%20chief%20economist%20Torsten%20Sl%C3%B8k%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20highlighted%2C%20there's%20a%20risk%20that%20those%20assumed%20rate%20cuts%20cause%20an%20inflation%20spike.%20And%20what's%20the%20best%20remedy%20for%20high%20inflation%3F%20Rate%20%3Cem%3Ehikes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20could%20throw%20a%20serious%20wrench%20into%20best-laid%20bullish%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELet's%20wrap%20up%20by%20throwing%20our%20hat%20in%20the%20prediction%20ring.%20I%20love%20a%20same-game%20parlay%2C%20so%20I'll%20offer%20a%20two-in-one%20pick.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20will%20drop%20below%206%2C000%20(about%20a%2015%25%20dip%20from%20current%20levels)%20before%20ultimately%20finishing%20the%20year%20above%207%2C200%20(about%205%25%20increase%20from%20where%20we%20are%20at).%20VIX%20traders%2C%20enjoy!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJoe%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWow!%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%20something%20no%20major%20Wall%20Street%20bank%20has%20had%20the%20guts%20to%20do%20yet%3A%20predict%20an%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20decline%20for%20next%20year.%20Under%20my%20scenario%20(let's%20say%206%2C850%2C%20about%200.2%25%20below%20current%20levels)%2C%20investors%20won't%20get%20as%20many%20rate%20cuts%20as%20they're%20currently%20banking%20on%2C%20even%20with%20a%20new%20Fed%20chair.%20Like%20the%20AI%20trade%2C%20rate-cut%20expectations%20are%20priced%20to%20perfection.%20I%20think%20that'll%20be%20spoiled%20by%20something%20unforeseen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20I%20end%20up%20being%20wrong%2C%20this%20conversation%20never%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYeah%2C%20call%20me%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D27b61d08cbe1aa9fae19bb86eda3cce9177c78e79e6a70a142a6eac721a3854b%26postID%3D69335c30addd14a892c6ba8e%26postSlug%3Dbi-today-newsletter-why-wall-streets-2026-predictions-matter-2025-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Fcollege-football%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F47182491%252Flane-kiffin-final-days-ole-miss-move-lsu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELane%20Kiffin%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I'm%20already%20moving%20on%20to%20the%20next%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-newsletter-why-wall-streets-2026-predictions-matter-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765203186000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69335c5e71107c9f3457796c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-newsletter-why-wall-streets-2026-predictions-matter-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bank%20strategists%20are%20weighing%20in%20on%20where%20they%20see%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20landing%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-newsletter-why-wall-streets-2026-predictions-matter-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%2