%20and%20dominance%20in%20global%20exports.%20China%20has%20successfully%20restructured%20its%20supply%20chains%2C%20rerouted%20exports%20to%20emerging%20markets%2C%20and%20leveraged%20currency%20advantages%20to%20bypass%20tariff%20barriers%2C%20outmaneuvering%20US%20trade%20war%20strategies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uber's%20latest%20play%20for%20ad%20dollars%3A%20turning%20data%20about%20your%20trips%20and%20takeout%20into%20insights%20for%20marketers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22uber%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6936854671107c9f34577f3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222554%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUber%20offers%20ads%20in%20its%20app%2C%20on%20in-car%20screens%2C%20and%20on%20vehicles.%20%3Cp%3EArtur%20Widak%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUber%20is%20launching%20an%20insights%20platform%20for%20marketers%20called%20Uber%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20has%20partnered%20with%20LiveRamp%20to%20aggregate%20users'%20data%20without%20revealing%20their%20identities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUber%20has%20said%20its%20ad%20business%20is%20on%20track%20to%20generate%20%241.5%20billion%20in%20revenue%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20wants%20advertisers%20to%20level%20up%20their%20marketing%20by%20tapping%20into%20data%20on%20the%20millions%20of%20rides%20and%20deliveries%20its%20users%20order%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ride-hailing%20giant%20is%20announcing%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20new%20insights%20platform%20called%20Uber%20Intelligence%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20company%20exclusively%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20data-connectivity%20platform%20LiveRamp%2C%20Uber%20Intelligence%20will%20let%20advertisers%20securely%20combine%20their%20customer%20data%20with%20Uber's%20to%20help%20surface%20insights%20about%20their%20audiences%2C%20based%20on%20what%20they%20eat%20and%20where%20they%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20uses%20LiveRamp's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-adtech-firms-leading-the-charge-in-how-advertising-data-is-used-2021-7%23liveramp-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclean%20room%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20lets%20companies%20aggregate%20their%20data%20in%20a%20privacy-safe%20environment%2C%20without%20sharing%20or%20seeing%20each%20other's%20raw%20or%20personally%20identifiable%20customer%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20hotel%20brand%20could%20use%20Uber%20Intelligence%20to%20help%20identify%20which%20restaurants%20or%20entertainment%20venues%20it%20might%20want%20to%20partner%20with%20for%20its%20loyalty%20program%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20also%20hopes%20the%20platform%20can%20act%20as%20a%20flywheel%20for%20its%20broader%20ad%20business.%20Marketers%20can%20use%20the%20data%20clean%20room%20for%20segmentation%2C%20such%20as%20identifying%20customers%20who%20are%20heavy%20business%20travelers%2C%20then%20targeting%20them%20with%20ads%20on%20their%20next%20trip%20to%20the%20airport%20in%20the%20Uber%20app%20or%20on%20screens%20inside%20Uber%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20seamlessness%20is%20why%20we're%20so%20excited%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwin%20Wong%2C%20global%20head%20of%20measurement%20at%20Uber%20Advertising%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20aim%20is%20for%20marketers%20to%20begin%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B'Oh%2C%20I'm%20not%20just%20understanding%20Uber%2C%20I'm%20understanding%20Uber%20in%20my%20marketing%20context.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242ba9d9a-79c8-4251-aa36-0bf02422f1ea%5C%22%3EUber's%20other%20route%20to%20revenue%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20Intelligence%20is%20the%20latest%20step%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ads-plans-1-billion-revenue-2024-investor-presentation-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber's%20ad%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Uber%20officially%20launched%20its%20dedicated%20advertising%20division%20in%202022.%20It%20offers%20an%20array%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ads-plans-1-billion-revenue-2024-investor-presentation-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ead%20formats%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Uber%20and%20Uber%20Eats%20apps%2C%20on%20in-car%20tablets%2C%20in%20emails%20to%20its%20users%2C%20and%20on%20car%20tops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20in%20May%20that%20its%20ad%20business%20had%20reached%20a%20%241.5%20billion%20revenue%20run%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20the%20figure%20it%20has%20projected%20to%20hit%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025%20%E2%80%94%20which%20would%20represent%20a%2060%25%20increase%20on%20last%20year.%20The%20company%20doesn't%20break%20out%20a%20more%20specific%20ad-revenue%20figure%20and%20hasn't%20provided%20an%20update%20on%20the%20run-rate%20number%20since%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20Intelligence%20forms%20part%20of%20a%20bespoke%20set%20of%20services%20it%20offers%20its%20top%20advertisers.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20it%20launched%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-offers-ads-let-brands-pay-for-users-rides-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreative%20studio%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20brands%20can%20partner%20with%20Uber%20to%20deliver%20more%20bespoke%20campaigns%2C%20such%20as%20offering%20rides%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiami-grand-prix-distinct-features-f1-race-marina-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMiami%20F1%20Grand%20Prix%20attendees%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20luxury%20vehicle%20sponsored%20by%20La%20Mer%2C%20packed%20with%20freebie%20skincare%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Frank%2C%20analyst%20at%20the%20research%20firm%20Gartner%2C%20said%20the%20launch%20of%20Uber%20Intelligence%20is%20another%20signal%20that%20Uber's%20ad%20business%20is%20maturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarly-stage%20ad%20businesses%20tend%20to%20focus%20exclusively%20on%20selling%20inventory%20while%20more%20mature%20ones%20focus%20more%20on%20delivering%20differentiated%20value%20through%20targeting%20and%20measurement%20solutions%20that%20help%20brands%20understand%20and%20optimize%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20spend%2C%26quot%3B%20Frank%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber's%20unique%20source%20of%20%26quot%3Bterrestrial%20data%26quot%3B%20put%20it%20in%20good%20standing%20against%20the%20likes%20of%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20other%20retail%20media%20networks%20that%20emphasize%20the%20value%20of%20their%20data-driven%20insights%2C%20Frank%20added.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20Uber%20may%20need%20to%20address%20privacy%20concerns%20related%20to%20aggregating%20highly%20sensitive%20data%20in%20order%20to%20maintain%20consumer%20trust%20and%20to%20comply%20with%20evolving%20global%20regulators%20as%20a%20collector%20of%20first-party%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVihan%20Sharma%2C%20chief%20revenue%20officer%20of%20LiveRamp%2C%20said%20its%20platform%20provides%20technical%20guarantees%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bzero%20movement%20of%20data.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20objective%20of%20a%20clean%20room%20technology%20is%20to%20build%20trust%20between%20data%20owners%20and%20consumers%20and%20the%20advertising%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ads-launches-intelligence-insights-trips-takeout-data-marketers-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765202461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693685ba71107c9f34577f45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%