ique%20experiences%20you're%20facing%20with%20your%20student%20loans.%20Do%20you%20have%20a%20student-loan%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Please%20fill%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flnkd.in%2FeDDHUjmJ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20form%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20we'll%20be%20in%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers%20wrote%20in%20their%20letters%20to%20the%20federal%20servicers%20that%2C%20given%20the%20slew%20of%20changes%2C%20it's%20imperative%20that%20borrowers%20can%20receive%20help%20from%20their%20servicers%2C%20along%20with%20accurate%20paperwork%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudent%20loan%20servicers'%20administrative%20errors%20have%20significant%20financial%20consequences%20for%20borrowers%2C%20including%20delayed%20rent%20payments%2C%20loss%20of%20mortgage%20eligibility%2C%20postponed%20retirement%20contributions%2C%20and%20even%20risk%20of%20homelessness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawmakers%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBorrowers%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20servicers'%20neglect%20and%20incompetence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20wrote%20in%20its%202024%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.consumerfinance.gov%2Ff%2Fdocuments%2Fcfpb_2024-annual-student-loan-ombudsmans-report_2024-11.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20servicer%20errors%2C%20such%20as%20incorrect%20payment%20processing%20and%20difficulties%20contacting%20customer%20service%20agents%2C%20led%20to%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20downstream%20consequences%26quot%3B%20that%20caused%20borrowers%20to%20be%20late%20on%20their%20monthly%20bills%20and%20even%20put%20some%20at%20risk%20of%20homelessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-trump-cfpb-decision-make-future-student-loan-forgiveness-harder-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehalting%20the%20CFPB's%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20lawmakers%20wrote%20that%20borrowers%20are%20at%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20being%20scammed%20by%20actors%20posing%20as%20federal%20servicers%2C%20enhancing%20the%20need%20for%20clear%20servicer%20communication.%20They%20requested%20that%20the%20servicers%20answer%20a%20series%20of%20questions%20by%20December%2022%2C%20including%20data%20on%20call%20center%20volume%2C%20staffing%20numbers%2C%20and%20communications%20to%20borrowers%20in%20delinquency%20or%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20loan%20repayment%20due%20dates%20and%20requirements%20have%20changed%20repeatedly%20for%20many%20borrowers%20under%20the%20Trump%20Administration%2C%20borrowers%20need%20clear%20and%20timely%20communication%20from%20federal%20student%20loan%20servicers%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200e38ce8-350b-4713-80fc-f049d9abcaa2%5C%22%3EThe%20consequences%20of%20servicer%20errors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-uncertainty-payments-resuming-debt-relief-paperwork-issues-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECustomer%20service%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20plagued%20student-loan%20borrowers%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Education%20Department%20released%20a%20memo%20in%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-bills-are-wrong-borrowers-servicers-fixing-errors-education-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edetailing%20the%20errors%3C%2Fa%3E%20borrowers%20have%20experienced%20with%20their%20servicers.%20It%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payments-resume-confusion-borrowers-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincorrect%20monthly%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20late%20or%20no%20billing%20statements%2C%20mistakenly%20taking%20borrowers%20out%20of%20forbearance%2C%20and%20long%20hold%20times%20with%20customer%20agents.%20The%20mistakes%20were%20costly%