to%20save%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20wealth%20advisor%20explained%20to%20me%20that's%20not%20how%20you%20grow%20wealth.%20She%20worked%20with%20me%20at%20a%20slow%20pace.%20First%2C%20we%20put%20money%20in%20a%20CD%20account%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20savings%20account.%20Once%20I%20was%20comfortable%20with%20that%2C%20we%20moved%20on%20to%20stocks.%20I'm%20still%20learning%20as%20I%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20my%20daughter%20chooses%20whether%20she%20wants%20to%20ride%20to%20school%20in%20my%20pink%20Mercedes%20G%20Wagon%2C%20my%20blue%20Corvette%2C%20or%20one%20of%20my%20other%20cars.%20She's%20living%20a%20life%20I%20couldn't%20imagine%20at%20her%20age%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20the%20cars%20are%20mostly%20a%20business%20tool%20for%20when%20we%20do%20influencer%20marketing%20shoots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20encourage%20my%20daughter's%20dreams.%20Currently%2C%20she%20wants%20to%20create%20content%20online%2C%20so%20I%20purchased%20the%20necessary%20equipment%20for%20her.%20She%20and%20I%20are%20both%20in%20therapy%2C%20and%20we're%20doing%20the%20work%20to%20break%20family%20cycles%20of%20domestic%20violence.%20I'm%20proud%20of%20everything%20I've%20accomplished%2C%20but%20finding%20the%20strength%20to%20break%20free%20is%20my%20greatest%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-built-multimillion-dollar-brand-as-a-single-mom-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765194249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F692ddc8aabd5e944effbd0cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-built-multimillion-dollar-brand-as-a-single-mom-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Glamlite%20founder%20Gisselle%20Hernandez%20shares%20how%20motherhood%20motivated%20her%20to%20build%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20beauty%20brand%20and%20redefine%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40ins