h2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Ottawa%20signed%20a%20comprehensive%20free-trade%20agreement%20with%20Indonesia%2C%20the%20first%20with%20the%20Asian%20Pacific%20country.%20Two%20months%20later%2C%20Canada%20secured%20a%20bilateral%20investment%20treaty%20with%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20that%20came%20with%20an%20expanded%20air-services%20pact.%20Canada%20is%20also%20fast-tracking%20a%20previously%20stalled%20trade%20agreement%20with%20India%20and%20pushing%20for%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20with%20the%20entirety%20of%20ASEAN%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20campaign%20page%20promoting%20foreign%20investment%20had%20appeared%20by%20August%20on%20the%20Canadian%20government%20website%2C%20featuring%20a%20slogan%20that%20reads%2C%20%26quot%3BDiversification%20is%20a%20national%20imperative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeredith%20Lilly%2C%20professor%20of%20international%20affairs%20at%20Carleton%20University%20and%20a%20former%20International%20Trade%20Advisor%20to%20former%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Stephen%20Harper%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20even%20though%20some%20negotiations%20with%20Asian%20countries%20have%20been%20in%20the%20works%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20current%20government%20of%20Canada%20is%20touting%20the%20efforts%20that%20the%20country%20is%20making%20and%20accelerating%20them%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bresponse%20to%20slow%20and%20difficult%20negotiations%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20very%20difficult%20administration%20to%20work%20with%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lilly%20of%20Trump's%20team.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20should%20have%20no%20expectation%20that%20these%20diversification%20efforts%20can%20move%20quickly%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20project%20that%20we%20should%20always%20be%20undertaking%2C%20and%20we%20should%20be%20working%20on%20it%20consistently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20more%20that%20Canada%20can%20do%2C%20too%2C%20Lilly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20Canada%20can%20do%20more%20quickly%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20US%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etariffs'%20impact%20on%20the%20economy%20is%20to%20increase%20trade%20relations%20with%20countries%20it%20already%20has%20agreements%20with.%20That%20includes%20Korea%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20the%2012%20Pacific%20Rim%20countries%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Trans-Pacific%20Partnership%2C%20Lilly%20said%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20highly%20interested%20in%20Canada's%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Canada%20Energy%20Regulator%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-tariff-exports-canada-mexico-oil-autos-electronics-machinery-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECanadian%20oil%20exports%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20the%20US%20reached%20a%20record%20525%2C000%20barrels%20per%20day%20in%20July%202025%20and%20remain%20elevated%20throughout%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanada%2C%20while%20initially%20expecting%20a%20larger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyale-budget-report-canada-gdp-suffer-most-trump-tariff-damage-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehit%20on%20the%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20Trump's%20tariffs%2C%20has%20also%20reported%20surprisingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-canada-economy-tariffs-trade-war-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobust%20GDP%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20the%20country%20reported%20a%202.6%25%20GDP%20growth%20rate%2C%20according%20to%20Statistics%20Canada%2C%20surpassing%20a%20previously%20revised%201.8%25%20projection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244fa4373-6d96-42d0-8201-7105334fec2d%5C%22%3EA%20decline%20in%20confidence%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECarlo%20Dade%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20International%20Policy%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Public%20Policy%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Calgary%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20may%20not%20be%20worth%20it%20to%20make%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20US%20now%2C%20because%20most%20Canadian%20goods%20are%20covered%20by%20the%20existing%20USMCA%20trade%20agreement%2C%20and%20because%20many%20of%20Trump's%20foreign%20policy%20moves%20seem%20%26quot%3Bpersonal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20argue%20that%20we%20shouldn't%20be%20trying%20to%20get%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dade.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20what%20happened%20to%20Malaysia%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20if%20that's%20a%20deal%2C%20do%20you%20want%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalaysia%20and%20Vietnam%2C%20despite%20agreeing%20to%20remove%20most%20tariffs%20on%20the%20US%2C%20still%20ended%20up%20with%2019%25%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-strikes-vietnam-deal-tariff-nike-lululemon-price-hike-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E20%25%20of%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20respectively.%20The%20UK%2C%20despite%20having%20secured%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-deal-tariffs-uk-announcement-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20deal%20with%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20fairly%20early%20in%20the%20year%2C%20is%20not%20exempt%20from%20a%20general%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20most%20goods%20and%20a%2025%25%20duty%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20gets%20a%20good%20deal%20from%20Trump.%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fart-of-deal-tariffs-trump-lessons-from-book-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Art%20of%20the%20Deal%3C%2Fa%3E'%20says%20there%20are%20winners%20and%20there%20are%20losers%2C%20and%20the%20US%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20winner%2C%26quot%3B%20Dade%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20Trump's%20book%20on%20dealmaking%20strategies.%20%26quot%3BSo%20what%20you're%20looking%20for%20is%20not%20a%20good%20deal.%20You're%20looking%20for%20the%20least%20worst%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuck%20said%20that%20even%20though%20the%20US%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20leverage%20over%20its%20closest%20trading%20partners%2C%20he%20is%20concerned%20about%20the%20long-term%20reputational%20damage%20the%20country%20will%20suffer%20among%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20you%20have%20the%20biggest%20stick%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20have%20to%20use%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Luck.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20insist%20on%20cashing%20in%20on%20all%20your%20leverage%20today%2C%20you%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20you%20have%20the%20most%20ability%20to%20harm%20and%20therefore%20the%20most%20leverage%20over%20your%20closest%20allies%20and%20partners%20whose%20trade%20is%20most%20integrated%20with%20yours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-courting-asia-after-a-year-of-trade-trump-tariffs-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765192442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F692e0c0e71107c9f34571fb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-courting-asia-after-a-year-of-trade-trump-tariffs-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20international%20trade%20experts%20in%20Canada%20are%20questioning%20if%20the%20country%20should%20still%20be%20trying%20to%20reach%20deal%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-courting-asia-after-a-year-of-trade-trump-tariffs-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thousands%20flee%20Thai-Cambodia%20border%20after%20deadly%20clashes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765192230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F