years%20upskilling%20to%20transition%20to%20an%20AI%20role%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20started%20reading%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20books%20during%20paternity%20leave%20to%20kick%20off%20his%20job%20pivot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20continuous%20learning%2C%20hands-on%20projects%2C%20and%20support%20were%20key%20to%20his%20transition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Rahul%20Kasanagottu%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20customer%20engineer%20at%20Google%2C%20specialized%20in%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20and%20based%20in%20Austin.%20His%20identity%20and%20employment%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20following%20has%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20few%20years%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20a%20customer%20success%20role%20at%20Google%2C%20but%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-engineer-said-landing-ai-role-took-year-daily-upskilling-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%20train%20came%20along%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20pivotal%20moments%20in%20technology%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20go%20into%20it%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20money.%20I%20think%20more%20people%20should%20think%20about%20getting%20into%20AI%20to%20help%20influence%20how%20it%20will%20be%20used%20by%20others%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20was%20born%20in%20April%202023%2C%20and%20the%20AI%20boom%20hit%20right%20around%20then.%20Google%20offers%20generous%20parental%20leave%2C%20and%20I%20figured%20it%20would%20be%20a%20good%20opportunity%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20daughter%20and%20start%20re