%20crochet%20brand%20focuses%20on%20the%20emotional%20value%20of%20each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzains_story%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZain%E2%80%99s%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Manya%2C%20Zainab%E2%80%99s%20idea%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20from%20a%20specific%20request.%20It%20was%20born%20out%20of%20her%20own%20reflections%20on%20weddings%20and%20memory.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20moment.%20It%20was%20just%20the%20thought%20that%20you%20could%20preserve%20your%20special%20day%20in%20a%20more%20meaningful%20way.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20began%20curating%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%2C%20she%20says%2C%20has%20been%20steadily%20growing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20off%20immediately%2C%20but%20now%20I%20get%20new%20queries%20almost%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%20Each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Etakes%20two%20to%20three%20days%20to%20make%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20flowers%20and%20the%20design.%20She%20uses%20acrylic%20yarn%20and%20adds%20beads%20to%20bind%20the%20flowers%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zainab%2C%20the%20appeal%20lies%20in%20the%20emotional%20value.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20goes%20to%20waste.%20The%20flowers%20don%E2%80%99t%20wilt.%20It%E2%80%99s%20handmade%20with%20love%20and%20care%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20couples%20can%20keep%20forever.%20I%20feel%20weddings%20are%20moving%20towards%20more%20sustainable%2C%20mindful%20choices%2C%20and%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efit%20right%20into%20that.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20how%20sentimental%20they%20are%20and%20full%20of%20soul.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20crochet%2C%20why%20now%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20crochet