der%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20yield%20per%20acre%20may%20be%20slightly%20lower%20compared%20to%20conventional%20seeds%2C%20the%20overall%20benefits%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326709%2Fcultyvate-agri-tech-solution-helps-paddy-farmers-reduce-water-waste-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduced%20input%20costs%20and%20improved%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20far%20outweigh%20any%20minor%20differences%20in%20productivity.%20Besides%2C%20I%20am%20earning%20Rs%202%2C600%20per%20quintal%20instead%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20rates%20for%20regular%20wheat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Sukhwinder%2C%20at%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20thanks%20to%20Aishwarya%20and%20Prateek%20Rastogi%2C%20who%20are%20promoting%20innovative%20and%20eco-friendly%20farming%20methods%20that%20benefit%20both%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20food%20we%20eat%20daily%20nutritious%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20after%20completing%20higher%20studies%20and%20gaining%20entrepreneurship%20training%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Prateek%20felt%20a%20strong%20calling%20towards%20uplifting%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20in%20his%20home%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20advised%20to%20venture%20into%20more%20developed%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%20and%20Gujarat%20for%20ease%20of%20business%2C%20he%20strived%20to%20focus%20on%20central%20and%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20regions%20that%20still%20required%20substantial%20advancement%20in%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20for%20the%20corporate%20world%20for%20a%20year%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20moved%20to%20his%20ancestral%20village%20in%20Sitapur%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Aishwarya%2C%20who%20is%20an%20alumna%20of%20IHM%20Bombay%20where%20she%20studied%20food%20sciences%20and%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20out%20to%20live%20out%20of%20an%20agri-warehouse.%20This%20is%20where%20they%20learnt%20more%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342901%2Ffarmer-income-success-lcb-fertilizers-biofertiliser-navyakosh-akshay-shrivastav-iit-kanpur-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenges%20faced%20by%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRural%20visits%20are%20close%20to%20our%20hearts.%20We%20love%20spending%20time%20in%20villages%2C%20cooking%20by%20a%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20chulha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(firewood%20stove)%2C%20and%20sharing%20stories%20with%20farmers.%20I%20also%20grew%20up%20eating%20farm%20produce%20that%20was%20sent%20to%20us%20from%20our%20village%20to%20our%20home%20in%20Lucknow.%20These%20experiences%20fuel%20our%20passion%20for%20our%20startup%20and%20our%20commitment%20to%20improving%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20farming%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20he%20observed%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20farmers%20toil%20day%20and%20night%20to%20grow%20food%2C%20it%20lacks%20sufficient%20nutritional%20content.%20India%20faces%20severe%20micronutrient%20deficiencies%20due%20to%20essential%20nutrients%20lacking%20in%20crop%20outputs%2C%20leading%20to%20health%20issues%20like%20anaemia%20and%20stunted%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20At%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%2